sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as AppMobile
    participant LocalDB
    participant Geofence
    participant API
    participant Queue as AudioQueue
    User->>App: Open Map
    App->>LocalDB: Load cached POIs
    LocalDB-->>App: Cached POIs
    App->>API: GET /api/poi + /api/poi/nearby
    API-->>App: POIs
    App->>Geofence: Start location polling
    Geofence-->>App: In-range POI list
    App->>Queue: Enqueue in-range POIs
    Queue-->>App: Next POI to play
    App->>API: GET /api/audio/poi/{id}
    API-->>App: Audio URL by language
    alt no audio file
        App->>App: TTS fallback from narration text
    end
    App->>User: Play narration
